<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Sends Gift to Kim Chong-il </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sends Gift to Kim Chong-il </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1405112794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1046 GMT 14 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1405112794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 14 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade 
Kim Chong-il, chairman of the National Defence Commission of the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea and supreme commander of 
the Korean People's Army, received a gift from a high-level 
delegation of the Ministry of National Defence of Laos on a 
visit to Korea. 
  The gift was handed to member of the Political Bureau of the 
C.C. [Central Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea and Chief 
of the General Staff of the Korean People's Army Choe Kwang by 
member of the Political Bureau of the Central Committee of the 
Lao People's Revolutionary Party and Minister of National 
Defence Sai-ngason Choummali. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

