<H3> <TI>   Kim Il-song's Works Carried by Foreign Papers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kim Il-song's Works Carried by Foreign Papers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1605050594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0432 GMT 16 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1605050594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 16 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song's famous work "Answers to the Questions 
Raised by the U.S. CNN News Coverage Group" was reported by the 
Maltese paper L'ORIZZONT, the Russian paper VECHERNAYA MOSKVA 
and the Hungarian paper SZABADSAG. 
  The Maltese and Russian papers printed portraits of 
President 
Kim Il-song. 
  The work "10-point Programme of the Great Unity of the Whole 
Nation for the Reunification of the Country" was carried by the 
Nicaraguan paper AVANCE, and the work "On Further Developing the 
Communist Policy" by the Mongolian paper UNEN. 

</TEXT>

