<H3> <TI>   Soldiers Help Build Chongpung River Bridge </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Soldiers Help Build Chongpung River Bridge </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1605105694 Pyongyang Korean Central Television Network in 
Korean 1100 GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1605105694 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Soldiers of the Korea People's Army unit to which 
Comrade Sin Sung-chik belongs are striving for the construction 
of the Pyongyang-Hyangsan Expressway upholding the order from 
the respected and beloved comrade supreme commander. The 
soldiers are putting more efforts in the construction of the 
Chongpung River Bridge. The soldiers have accelerated the 
construction in their resolve to complete the newly built 
Chongpung River Bridge as a modern creation of the chuche era. 
Recently, they are vigorously accelerating concreting the road 
after completing the V-type pillar in early April. 
  Technician functionaries of the unit are strengthening 
guidance to every process of the construction while making 
higher demands for all the soldiers to guarantee the 
construction quality. The soldiers are also speeding up the 
construction bearing an iron-like faith that "What the party 
decides, we will do." 

</TEXT>

