<F P=105>  Burmese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A seven-member delegation from the People's 
Republic of China led by Mr. He Zhiqiang, governor of Yunnan 
Province, arrived in Yangon [Rangoon] by air from Bangkok this 
