repatriated from Sanaa. Foreign Affairs Secretary Roberto 
Romulo said this is with the understanding that the respective 
employers will certify their allowing their workers to leave. 
In these countries, as a matter policy, require foreign 
employees will get out of their territories to secure exit 
visas. [sentence as heard] 
  The government is now faced with funding problems with the 
evacuation and repatriation of Filipino workers in Yemen. 
Foreign Affairs Secretary Roberto Romulo says that they are now 
looking for other resources to fund the repatriation of Filipino 
workers. 

