  [Text] Seoul, May 16 (YONHAP) -- The Communications 
Ministry sent a delegation to China Monday to discuss Korea's 
participation in projects for building a communications network 
in Hunan Province and laying a 3,600-kilometer fiber optic cable 
between Beijing and Guangzhou. 
  Bilateral cooperation in the two projects was agreed on at a 
