ministers' meeting in late March. 
  Hunan Province is asking Seoul for a 40-million-dollar loan 
out of the Economic Development and Cooperation Fund. The 
Chinese Government plans to spend 100 million dollars on the 
fiber optic cable project between Beijing and Guangzhou. 
  The Korean delegation, comprising officials from the 
Communications and Finance Ministries, Korea Telecom and other 
research institutes, will return May 21. 

